    <p>Vital Proteins uses Verisol bioactive collagen peptides — the specific collagen type used in the landmark clinical trials that demonstrated 20% wrinkle reduction and 65% increased procollagen production. The 2.5g dose matches the exact amount used in those studies. Combined with 120mg hyaluronic acid (clinical dose for skin moisture improvement) and vitamin C (essential collagen synthesis cofactor), this is the most evidence-backed skin gummy formula available. Vital Proteins' brand leadership in the collagen category (acquired by Nestle) provides manufacturing scale and quality assurance.</p>

