    </div>

    <p>Olly takes a unique approach with sea buckthorn — a berry rich in omega-7 fatty acids (palmitoleic acid) that support skin barrier function and mucous membrane health. Combined with hyaluronic acid, vitamin C, and vitamin E, Olly addresses skin health from multiple angles: structural support (collagen), hydration (HA), antioxidant defense (C + E), and barrier repair (sea buckthorn). The plum berry flavor is the best-tasting skin gummy in our evaluation. At $0.28/serving, it offers excellent value for a multi-ingredient formula.</p>

