    <p>HUM Nutrition formulates every product with a registered dietitian and triple-tests all ingredients for purity, potency, and environmental contaminants. The 240mg hyaluronic acid is double the dose of most competitors and at the upper end of clinically studied amounts for skin hydration. The grapeseed extract provides oligomeric proanthocyanidins (OPCs) — antioxidant compounds 20x more potent than vitamin C and 50x more potent than vitamin E at neutralizing free radicals. For maximum hydration and antioxidant protection without collagen, HUM provides the most potent formula.</p>

