    <p>Garden of Life sources grass-fed, pasture-raised bovine collagen and combines it with organic silica from bamboo — a trace mineral that provides the structural framework for collagen cross-linking. Silica strengthens the bonds between collagen fibers, enhancing the structural integrity of skin, hair, and nails. The vitamin C from organic acerola cherry provides the essential cofactor for collagen synthesis in a whole food form. For consumers who prioritize ethical sourcing, clean ingredients, and a whole-food approach to beauty supplementation, Garden of Life is the definitive choice.</p>

