      </div>
    </div>

    <p>SugarBear gained massive popularity through influencer partnerships and social media marketing, but the formula does have merit. Evening primrose oil provides gamma-linolenic acid (GLA) — an omega-6 fatty acid that supports skin barrier function and reduces inflammation. Combined with grape seed extract antioxidants and a comprehensive skin vitamin blend (A, C, E, biotin, zinc), it provides a solid vitamin-based approach to skin health. The bear-shaped gummies and attractive packaging add an element of enjoyment to the daily routine. The premium pricing reflects influencer marketing costs rather than ingredient superiority.</p>

